{"tid":2074271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[藍店銀杏館]馬蹄露楊明姚瑩瑩等藍藝人到銀杏館做義工 派發愛心飯盒","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T02:53:33.000Z","uid":34410,"like":508,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f294b4409c1b827986c17742c91320b8ce0eaa","tid":2074271,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"社企銀杏館一直有支援有需要人士，為他們提供免費飯盒。日前藝人馬蹄露、楊明、莊思明等到銀杏館做義工派飯，又呼籲大家一起做義工。 <br />\n<br />\n銀杏館早前發起愛心抗疫飯盒行動，為長者、綜援人士、露宿者等有需要人士派發愛心飯盒，希望協助他們在疫境中仍能得到溫飽。藝人馬蹄露今早於Facebook發帖指歡迎大家前往銀杏館做義工。從相片所見，除馬蹄露外，楊明、莊思明、姚瑩瑩、李霖恩等亦有同行，分別為銀杏館包裝飯盒或作登記、派飯。 <br />\n<br />\n不少網民盛讚馬蹄露有善心，又有人表示要加入義工行列。馬蹄露回覆指若大家有興趣可致電給油麻地銀杏館阿Ray，查詢相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOeyYAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOeyYAf.jpg&h=f5c094e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBEvgnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBEvgnb.png&h=f1533b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chQa0OU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchQa0OU.png&h=cef5f3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬蹄露，楊明、莊思明、姚瑩瑩、李霖恩，成班都藍到發黑<br />\n銀杏館咩立場自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13484111417b2313a667b1d6d3f0b2edfe66247e","tid":2074271,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"罷食"},{"pid":"9e6506777ac3cba1f3cc69819422faeb6e5c1cc7","tid":2074271,"uid":204539,"like":307,"dislike":1,"score":306,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:41:05.000Z","msg":"原來係狗飯工場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1fd794fc7176fe07ffeedf4fd00738fa9391fa","tid":2074271,"uid":47674,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:41:23.000Z","